## вҖӢеҸҰи«ӢеҸғй–ұ







з°ЎеҢ–зҡ„ V2 TypeScript Agent SDK й җиҰҪпјҢе…·жңүз”Ёж–јеӨҡијӘе°Қи©ұзҡ„еҹәж–јжңғи©ұзҡ„ send/stream жЁЎејҸгҖӮ

V2 д»ӢйқўжҳҜдёҖеҖӢ **дёҚз©©е®ҡзҡ„й җиҰҪзүҲжң¬**гҖӮAPI еҸҜиғҪжңғж №ж“ҡеҸҚйҘӢйҖІиЎҢжӣҙж”№пјҢз„¶еҫҢжүҚиғҪи®ҠжҲҗз©©е®ҡзүҲжң¬гҖӮжҹҗдәӣеҠҹиғҪпјҲеҰӮжңғи©ұеҲҶеҸүпјүеғ…еңЁ [V1 SDK](https://code.claude.com/docs/zh-TW/agent-sdk/typescript) дёӯеҸҜз”ЁгҖӮ
V2 Claude Agent TypeScript SDK ж¶ҲйҷӨдәҶе°ҚйқһеҗҢжӯҘз”ҹжҲҗеҷЁе’Ң yield еҚ”иӘҝзҡ„йңҖжұӮгҖӮйҖҷдҪҝеӨҡијӘе°Қи©ұи®Ҡеҫ—жӣҙз°Ўе–®пјҢиҖҢдёҚжҳҜеңЁеҗ„ијӘд№Ӣй–“з®ЎзҗҶз”ҹжҲҗеҷЁзӢҖж…ӢпјҢжҜҸдёҖијӘйғҪжҳҜдёҖеҖӢе–®зҚЁзҡ„ `send()`/ `stream()` йҖұжңҹгҖӮAPI иЎЁйқўзё®жёӣзӮәдёүеҖӢжҰӮеҝөпјҡ


- `createSession()` / `resumeSession()`пјҡй–Ӣе§ӢжҲ–з№јзәҢе°Қи©ұ
- `session.send()`пјҡзҷјйҖҒиЁҠжҒҜ
- `session.stream()`пјҡеҸ–еҫ—еӣһжҮү


## [вҖӢ](https://code.claude.com/docs/zh-TW/agent-sdk/typescript-v2-preview#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%9D) е®үиЈқ


V2 д»ӢйқўеҢ…еҗ«еңЁзҸҫжңүзҡ„ SDK еҘ—д»¶дёӯпјҡ


```
npm install @anthropic-ai/claude-agent-sdk
```


SDK зӮәжӮЁзҡ„е№іеҸ°жҚҶз¶ҒдәҶдёҖеҖӢеҺҹз”ҹ Claude Code дәҢйҖІдҪҚжӘ”жЎҲдҪңзӮәеҸҜйҒёдҫқиіҙй …пјҢеӣ жӯӨжӮЁз„ЎйңҖе–®зҚЁе®үиЈқ Claude CodeгҖӮ


## [вҖӢ](https://code.claude.com/docs/zh-TW/agent-sdk/typescript-v2-preview#%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E9%96%8B%E5%A7%8B) еҝ«йҖҹй–Ӣе§Ӣ


### [вҖӢ](https://code.claude.com/docs/zh-TW/agent-sdk/typescript-v2-preview#%E5%96%AE%E6%AC%A1%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA) е–®ж¬ЎжҸҗзӨә


е°Қж–јдёҚйңҖиҰҒз¶ӯиӯ·жңғи©ұзҡ„з°Ўе–®е–®ијӘжҹҘи©ўпјҢи«ӢдҪҝз”Ё `unstable_v2_prompt()`гҖӮжӯӨзҜ„дҫӢзҷјйҖҒдёҖеҖӢж•ёеӯёе•ҸйЎҢдёҰиЁҳйҢ„зӯ”жЎҲпјҡ


```
import { unstable_v2_prompt } from "@anthropic-ai/claude-agent-sdk";

const result = await unstable_v2_prompt("What is 2 + 2?", {
  model: "claude-opus-4-7"
});
if (result.subtype === "success") {
  console.log(result.result);
}
```


### [вҖӢ](https://code.claude.com/docs/zh-TW/agent-sdk/typescript-v2-preview#%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%9C%83%E8%A9%B1) еҹәжң¬жңғи©ұ


е°Қж–ји¶…еҮәе–®еҖӢжҸҗзӨәзҡ„дә’еӢ•пјҢи«Ӣе»әз«ӢдёҖеҖӢжңғи©ұгҖӮV2 е°ҮзҷјйҖҒе’ҢдёІжөҒеҲҶзӮәдёҚеҗҢзҡ„жӯҘй©ҹпјҡ


- `send()` еҲҶжҙҫжӮЁзҡ„иЁҠжҒҜ
- `stream()` дёІжөҒеӣһжҮү


йҖҷзЁ®жҳҺзўәзҡ„еҲҶйӣўдҪҝеҫ—еңЁијӘж¬Ўд№Ӣй–“ж·»еҠ йӮҸијҜи®Ҡеҫ—жӣҙе®№жҳ“пјҲдҫӢеҰӮеңЁзҷјйҖҒеҫҢзәҢиЁҠжҒҜд№ӢеүҚиҷ•зҗҶеӣһжҮүпјүгҖӮ
дёӢйқўзҡ„зҜ„дҫӢе»әз«ӢдёҖеҖӢжңғи©ұпјҢеҗ‘ Claude зҷјйҖҒгҖҢHello!гҖҚпјҢдёҰеҲ—еҚ°ж–Үеӯ—еӣһжҮүгҖӮе®ғдҪҝз”Ё [`await using`](https://www.typescriptlang.org/docs/handbook/release-notes/typescript-5-2.html#using-declarations-and-explicit-resource-management)пјҲTypeScript 5.2+пјүеңЁеҚҖеЎҠйҖҖеҮәжҷӮиҮӘеӢ•й—ңй–үжңғи©ұгҖӮжӮЁд№ҹеҸҜд»ҘжүӢеӢ•е‘јеҸ« `session.close()`гҖӮ


```
import { unstable_v2_createSession } from "@anthropic-ai/claude-agent-sdk";

await using session = unstable_v2_createSession({
  model: "claude-opus-4-7"
});

await session.send("Hello!");
for await (const msg of session.stream()) {
  // Filter for assistant messages to get human-readable output
  if (msg.type === "assistant") {
    const text = msg.message.content
      .filter((block) => block.type === "text")
      .map((block) => block.text)
      .join("");
    console.log(text);
  }
}
```


### [вҖӢ](https://code.claude.com/docs/zh-TW/agent-sdk/typescript-v2-preview#%E5%A4%9A%E8%BC%AA%E5%B0%8D%E8%A9%B1) еӨҡијӘе°Қи©ұ


жңғи©ұеңЁеӨҡж¬ЎдәӨжҸӣдёӯдҝқжҢҒдёҠдёӢж–ҮгҖӮиҰҒз№јзәҢе°Қи©ұпјҢи«ӢеңЁеҗҢдёҖжңғи©ұдёҠеҶҚж¬Ўе‘јеҸ« `send()`гҖӮClaude жңғиЁҳдҪҸд№ӢеүҚзҡ„ијӘж¬ЎгҖӮ
жӯӨзҜ„дҫӢи©ўе•ҸдёҖеҖӢж•ёеӯёе•ҸйЎҢпјҢз„¶еҫҢи©ўе•ҸдёҖеҖӢеј•з”Ёе…ҲеүҚзӯ”жЎҲзҡ„еҫҢзәҢе•ҸйЎҢпјҡ


```
import { unstable_v2_createSession } from "@anthropic-ai/claude-agent-sdk";

await using session = unstable_v2_createSession({
  model: "claude-opus-4-7"
});

// Turn 1
await session.send("What is 5 + 3?");
for await (const msg of session.stream()) {
  // Filter for assistant messages to get human-readable output
  if (msg.type === "assistant") {
    const text = msg.message.content
      .filter((block) => block.type === "text")
      .map((block) => block.text)
      .join("");
    console.log(text);
  }
}

// Turn 2
await session.send("Multiply that by 2");
for await (const msg of session.stream()) {
  if (msg.type === "assistant") {
    const text = msg.message.content
      .filter((block) => block.type === "text")
      .map((block) => block.text)
      .join("");
    console.log(text);
  }
}
```


### [вҖӢ](https://code.claude.com/docs/zh-TW/agent-sdk/typescript-v2-preview#%E6%9C%83%E8%A9%B1%E6%81%A2%E5%BE%A9) жңғи©ұжҒўеҫ©


еҰӮжһңжӮЁжңүдҫҶиҮӘе…ҲеүҚдә’еӢ•зҡ„жңғи©ұ IDпјҢжӮЁеҸҜд»ҘзЁҚеҫҢжҒўеҫ©е®ғгҖӮйҖҷе°Қж–јй•·жҷӮй–“йҒӢиЎҢзҡ„е·ҘдҪңжөҒзЁӢжҲ–з•¶жӮЁйңҖиҰҒеңЁжҮүз”ЁзЁӢејҸйҮҚж–°е•ҹеӢ•жҷӮдҝқжҢҒе°Қи©ұжҷӮеҫҲжңүз”ЁгҖӮ
жӯӨзҜ„дҫӢе»әз«ӢдёҖеҖӢжңғи©ұпјҢе„Іеӯҳе…¶ IDпјҢй—ңй–үе®ғпјҢз„¶еҫҢжҒўеҫ©е°Қи©ұпјҡ


```
import {
  unstable_v2_createSession,
  unstable_v2_resumeSession,
  type SDKMessage
} from "@anthropic-ai/claude-agent-sdk";

// Helper to extract text from assistant messages
function getAssistantText(msg: SDKMessage): string | null {
  if (msg.type !== "assistant") return null;
  return msg.message.content
    .filter((block) => block.type === "text")
    .map((block) => block.text)
    .join("");
}

// Create initial session and have a conversation
const session = unstable_v2_createSession({
  model: "claude-opus-4-7"
});

await session.send("Remember this number: 42");

// Get the session ID from any received message
let sessionId: string | undefined;
for await (const msg of session.stream()) {
  sessionId = msg.session_id;
  const text = getAssistantText(msg);
  if (text) console.log("Initial response:", text);
}

console.log("Session ID:", sessionId);
session.close();

// Later: resume the session using the stored ID
await using resumedSession = unstable_v2_resumeSession(sessionId!, {
  model: "claude-opus-4-7"
});

await resumedSession.send("What number did I ask you to remember?");
for await (const msg of resumedSession.stream()) {
  const text = getAssistantText(msg);
  if (text) console.log("Resumed response:", text);
}
```


### [вҖӢ](https://code.claude.com/docs/zh-TW/agent-sdk/typescript-v2-preview#%E6%B8%85%E7%90%86) жё…зҗҶ


жңғи©ұеҸҜд»ҘжүӢеӢ•й—ңй–үжҲ–дҪҝз”Ё [`await using`](https://www.typescriptlang.org/docs/handbook/release-notes/typescript-5-2.html#using-declarations-and-explicit-resource-management)пјҲTypeScript 5.2+ еҠҹиғҪз”Ёж–јиҮӘеӢ•иіҮжәҗжё…зҗҶпјүиҮӘеӢ•й—ңй–үгҖӮеҰӮжһңжӮЁдҪҝз”Ёзҡ„жҳҜијғиҲҠзҡ„ TypeScript зүҲжң¬жҲ–йҒҮеҲ°зӣёе®№жҖ§е•ҸйЎҢпјҢи«Ӣж”№з”ЁжүӢеӢ•жё…зҗҶгҖӮ
**иҮӘеӢ•жё…зҗҶпјҲTypeScript 5.2+пјүпјҡ**


```
import { unstable_v2_createSession } from "@anthropic-ai/claude-agent-sdk";

await using session = unstable_v2_createSession({
  model: "claude-opus-4-7"
});
// Session closes automatically when the block exits
```


**жүӢеӢ•жё…зҗҶпјҡ**


```
import { unstable_v2_createSession } from "@anthropic-ai/claude-agent-sdk";

const session = unstable_v2_createSession({
  model: "claude-opus-4-7"
});
// ... use the session ...
session.close();
```


## [вҖӢ](https://code.claude.com/docs/zh-TW/agent-sdk/typescript-v2-preview#api-%E5%8F%83%E8%80%83) API еҸғиҖғ


