```


### [вҖӢ](https://code.claude.com/docs/zh-TW/agent-sdk/typescript-v2-preview#unstable_v2_prompt) `unstable_v2_prompt()`


з”Ёж–је–®ијӘжҹҘи©ўзҡ„е–®ж¬ЎдҫҝеҲ©еҮҪж•ёгҖӮ


```
